<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Solicitud de viáticos aprobada</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; background-color: #f4f7f6; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .container { max-width: 640px; margin: 20px auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
    .urgent { background-color: #fef2f2; border-left: 6px solid #dc2626; padding: 12px 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #991b1b; }
    .header { background-color: #f8fafc; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
    .logo { max-width: 150px; height: auto; }
    .content { padding: 30px; }
    .heading { color: #1e293b; font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .details { background-color: #f8fafc; border-radius: 6px; padding: 15px; margin: 16px 0; border-left: 4px solid #22c55e; font-size: 14px; }
    .btn-container { text-align: center; margin-top: 24px; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background-color: #0ea5e9; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; }
    .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8; padding: 20px; background-color: #f8fafc; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="Viatika" class="logo">
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      {{#if urgent}}
      <div class="urgent">{{urgentBanner}}</div>
      {{/if}}
      <h1 class="heading">{{emailTitle}}</h1>
      <p>Estimado/a <strong>{{recipientName}}</strong>,</p>
      <p>Se ha <strong>aprobado</strong> una solicitud de viáticos. A continuación el detalle completo según alcance funcional.</p>
      <div class="details">{{{detailBody}}}</div>
      <div class="btn-container">
        <a href="{{platformUrl}}" class="btn">Ir a la plataforma</a>
      </div>
    </div></div>
</body>
</html>
